        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ ذَكَرَ اَللَّهَ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ فِي اَلْأَسْوَاقِ غَفَرَ لَهُ بِعَدَدِ أَهْلِهَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3756 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Whoever remembers Allah (swt), the Mighty and Exalted, in the marketplaces, Allah (swt) will forgive him by the number of its people.\""
        ]
